    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="basic"><a href="#basic" class="headerlink" title="basic"></a>basic</h1><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">文件第一行为指定内容：<span class="hljs-comment">#!/bin/bash</span><br>备注：<span class="hljs-comment">#</span><br>read：键盘输入参数内容<br><span class="hljs-literal">-x</span>:执行shell时可以查看执行的命令内容<br>shell执行方式：<span class="hljs-number">1</span>. bash   该方式不需要在脚本文件的第一行指定解释器信息，写了也没用<br>       <span class="hljs-number">2</span>. source或简写.  source 命令会强制执行脚本文件中的全部命令，而忽略脚本文件的权限。在当前线程中运行脚本<br>变量：例：var=<span class="hljs-number">123</span><br>变量在使用时才加<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>  ,赋值时不用<br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$var</span> 或 <span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;var&#125;&#123;&#125;可以帮助解释器识别变量的边界  如：<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;var&#125;iable与<span class="hljs-variable">$variable</span> 会解释为不同结果<br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>包围变量的值时，输出时会先解析里面的变量和命令 ,而<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>里面是什么就输出什么，内容原样输出<br>可以将命令执行后的结果赋给变量 var=`command` 或 var=<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>(command)<br>readonly可以将变量定义为只读变量，只读变量的值不能被改变  readonly var=<span class="hljs-number">11</span><br>local可以将变量定义为局部变量,只能在函数中使用<br>使用 unset 命令可以删除变量,变量被删除后不能再次使用；unset 命令不能删除只读变量<br>脚本中定义的变量默认为全局变量，作用范围为在当前脚本进程中有效，而不是当前脚本文件<br>export可以将变量变为环境变量，作用范围为当前shell进程及其子进程有效，父进程关闭时，环境变量会失效<br>特殊变量：<br><span class="hljs-variable">$0</span>当前脚本的文件名<br><span class="hljs-variable">$n</span>传递给脚本或函数的第几个参数<br><span class="hljs-variable">$</span><span class="hljs-comment">#传递给脚本或函数的个数</span><br><span class="hljs-variable">$</span>*传递给脚本或函数的所有参数<br><span class="hljs-variable">$</span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">@</span>传递给脚本或函数的所有参数<br>当被双引号<span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span>包含时，<span class="hljs-variable">$</span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">@</span> 与 <span class="hljs-variable">$</span>* 稍有不同<br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>*&quot;</span>会将所有的参数从整体上看做一份数据，而不是把每个参数都看做一份数据,如：<span class="hljs-number">123</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>@&quot;</span>仍然将每个参数都看作一份数据，彼此之间是独立的,如：<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span><br><span class="hljs-variable">$</span>?上个命令的退出状态，或函数的返回值<br><span class="hljs-variable">$</span><span class="hljs-variable">$</span>当前 Shell 进程 ID<br>数组：<br>赋值号=两边不能有空格，必须紧挨着数组名和数组元素,括号( )来表示数组，数组元素之间用空格来分隔,如：var=(<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span>)<br>长度不是固定的，定义之后还可以增加元素<br>无需逐个元素地给数组赋值,如：    ages=([<span class="hljs-number">3</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">24</span> [<span class="hljs-number">5</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">19</span> [<span class="hljs-number">10</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">12</span>)<br>获取数组元素值 <span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;array_name[<span class="hljs-type">index</span>])<br>使用<span class="hljs-selector-tag">@</span>或*可以获取数组中的所有元素  如：    <span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;array_name[*]&#125; 或  <span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;array_name[<span class="hljs-selector-tag">@</span>]&#125;<br>获取数组长度：  <span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">#array_name[*]&#125; 或  $&#123;#array_name[@]&#125;</span><br>数组拼接：array_new=(<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;array1[<span class="hljs-selector-tag">@</span>]&#125;  <span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;array2[<span class="hljs-selector-tag">@</span>]&#125;)  或  array_new=(<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;array1[*]&#125;  <span class="hljs-variable">$</span>&#123;array2[*]&#125;)<br>删除数组： unset array_name<br>数学计算：<br>(())用于整数运算，效率很高，推荐使用。如：((a=<span class="hljs-number">10</span>+<span class="hljs-number">66</span>) 注意，使用变量时不用加<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>前缀，(( )) 会自动解析变量名如：c=<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>((a+b))  类似 c=((a+b)) 这样的写法是错误的，不加<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>就不能取得表达式的结果<br>let用于整数运算，和 (()) 类似<br><span class="hljs-variable">$</span>[]用于整数运算，不如 (()) 灵活<br>expr可用于整数运算，也可以处理字符串。比较麻烦，需要注意各种细节，不推荐使用<br>bcLinux下的一个计算器程序，可以处理整数和小数,Shell 本身只支持整数运算，想计算小数就得使用 bc 这个外部的计算器。<br>declare将变量定义为整数，然后再进行数学运算时就不会被当做字符串了。功能有限，仅支持最基本的数学运算（加减乘除和取余），<br>不支持逻辑运算、自增自减等，所以在实际开发中很少使用。<br>检测条件是否成立：<br>(())   进行数值比较   &lt;  &gt;  =<br>test  也可简写为[]   test expression  或[ <span class="hljs-type">expression</span> ]  tip:[]和expression之间的空格，这两个空格是必须的。变量最好加上<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>避免为空时报错<br>数值比较(只适用于整数)： <span class="hljs-operator">-le</span> 小于等于；<span class="hljs-operator">-ge</span> 大于等于；<span class="hljs-operator">-lt</span> 小于；<span class="hljs-operator">-eq</span> 等于；<br>文件检测：文件类型：<span class="hljs-literal">-d</span> 文件是否存在且为目录；<span class="hljs-literal">-e</span> 文件是否存在；<br> 文件权限：<span class="hljs-literal">-r</span> 文件是否有读权限；<span class="hljs-literal">-w</span> ; <span class="hljs-literal">-x</span> ;<br> 文件比较：file1 <span class="hljs-literal">-nt</span> file2 判断file1修改时间是否比file2新；<br>逻辑运算：exp1 <span class="hljs-literal">-a</span> exp2 逻辑与； <span class="hljs-literal">-o</span> 逻辑或 ； ! 逻辑非<br>[[]]  比test更强大一些：变量不需要加<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> ;不能对&lt; &gt;转义；支持正则表达式 [[ <span class="hljs-type">str</span>=~<span class="hljs-type">regex</span> ]]；<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>截取字符串</strong>     </p><figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs elixir">例：var=<span class="hljs-symbol">http:</span>/<span class="hljs-regexp">/www.a.com/</span><span class="hljs-number">123</span>.html<br><span class="hljs-number">1</span>. <span class="hljs-comment">#  删除左边，保留右边</span><br><span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;</span>var<span class="hljs-comment">#*//&#125;    结果：www.a.com/123.html           *//表示从左边开始，删除到第一个//，包括//</span><br><span class="hljs-number">2</span>. <span class="hljs-comment">##  删除左边，保留右边</span><br><span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;</span>var<span class="hljs-comment">##*/&#125;   结果：123.html 从左边开始，删除到最后一个/，包括/</span><br><span class="hljs-number">3</span>. %  删除右边，保留左边<br><span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;</span>var%<span class="hljs-regexp">/*&#125;     结果：http:/</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/www.a.com  从右边开始，删除到第一个/</span>，包括/<br><span class="hljs-number">4</span>. %%  删除右边，保留左边<br><span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;</span>var%%<span class="hljs-regexp">/*&#125;    结果：http:从右边开始，删除到最后一个/</span>，包括/<br><span class="hljs-number">5</span>. 从左边第n个字符开始，截取m个字符<br><span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;</span><span class="hljs-symbol">var:</span>0<span class="hljs-symbol">:</span><span class="hljs-number">5</span>&#125;     结果：<span class="hljs-symbol">http:</span><br><span class="hljs-number">6</span>. 从左边第n个字符开始，截取一直到结束<br><span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;</span><span class="hljs-symbol">var:</span><span class="hljs-number">7</span>&#125;     结果：www.a.com/<span class="hljs-number">123</span>.html<br><span class="hljs-number">7</span>. 从右边第n个字符开始，截取m个字符<br><span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;</span><span class="hljs-symbol">var:</span>0<span class="hljs-number">-7</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:</span><span class="hljs-number">3</span>&#125;   结果：<span class="hljs-number">123</span><br><span class="hljs-number">8</span>. 从右边第n个字符开始，截取一直到结束<br><span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;</span><span class="hljs-symbol">var:</span>0<span class="hljs-number">-7</span>&#125;   结果：<span class="hljs-number">123</span>.html<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>获取字符串长度</strong>        </p><figure class="highlight excel"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs excel">例如：<span class="hljs-built_in">var</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;1234&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">1</span>.  $&#123;#<span class="hljs-built_in">var</span>&#125;    结果：<span class="hljs-number">4</span><br><span class="hljs-number">2</span>. expr length $&#123;<span class="hljs-built_in">var</span>&#125;   结果：<span class="hljs-number">4</span><br><span class="hljs-number">3</span>. expr $<span class="hljs-built_in">var</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;.*&quot;</span>  结果：<span class="hljs-number">4</span>    <span class="hljs-symbol">:</span>与$<span class="hljs-built_in">var</span>和<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.*&quot;</span>间有空格<br><span class="hljs-number">4</span>. echo $<span class="hljs-built_in">var</span> |wc -L    结果：<span class="hljs-number">4</span>       wc -L 单行字符串，表示当前行字符串长度；多行字符串，表示最长行的长度。<br><span class="hljs-number">5</span>. echo -<span class="hljs-built_in">n</span> $<span class="hljs-built_in">var</span> |wc -c   结果：<span class="hljs-number">4</span>     -<span class="hljs-built_in">n</span>表示去除“\n”换行符          wc  -c  表示统计字符的个数<br><span class="hljs-number">6</span>. echo  $<span class="hljs-built_in">var</span> |wc -c   结果：<span class="hljs-number">5</span>     区别在于-<span class="hljs-built_in">n</span>参数<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>选择结构</strong></p><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs csharp"><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>语句：<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>  condition<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>和then在同一行时，必须需要加;  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> condition ; <span class="hljs-function">then</span><br><span class="hljs-function">then</span><br><span class="hljs-function">    <span class="hljs-title">statement</span>(<span class="hljs-params">s</span>)</span><br><span class="hljs-function">fi</span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span>语句：</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> expression <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">    pattern1)</span><br><span class="hljs-function">        statement1</span><br>        ;;<br>    pattern2)<br>        statement2<br>        ;;<br>    *)<br>    statement<br>esac<br><span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span>支持的正则表达式：<br>* 任意字符串<br>[<span class="hljs-meta">abc</span>] 表示 a、b、c 三个字符中的任意一个<br>[<span class="hljs-meta">m-n</span>] 表示从 m 到 n 的任意一个字符<br>| 表示多重选择，类似逻辑运算中的或运算<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>循环结构</strong></p><figure class="highlight livecodeserver"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs livecodeserver"><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> condition条件成立执行<span class="hljs-built_in">do</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">do</span><br>    statements<br>done<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">until</span> condition条件不成立执行<span class="hljs-built_in">do</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">do</span><br>    statements<br>done<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>((<span class="hljs-built_in">exp1</span>; <span class="hljs-built_in">exp2</span>; exp3))<span class="hljs-built_in">exp1</span>、<span class="hljs-built_in">exp2</span>、exp3 是三个表达式，其中 <span class="hljs-built_in">exp2</span> 是判断条件，<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> 循环根据 <span class="hljs-built_in">exp2</span> 的结果来决定是否继续下一次循环<br><span class="hljs-built_in">do</span><br>    statements<br>done<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">variable</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> value_list<br><span class="hljs-built_in">do</span><br>    statements<br>done<br><br>select <span class="hljs-built_in">variable</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> value_list按下 Ctrl+D 组合键，结束 select <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> 循环<br><span class="hljs-built_in">do</span><br>    statements<br>done<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>函数</strong></p><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ada">定义：<br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">name</span>() &#123;<br>    statements<br>    [<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-type">value]</span><br>&#125;<br>简化写法：<br>name() &#123;可以不写 <span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">关键字</span><br>    statements<br>    [<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-type">value]</span><br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">name</span> &#123;写了 <span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">关键字，也可以省略函数名后面的小括号</span><br>    statements<br>    [<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-type">value]</span><br>&#125;<br><br>调用函数只用写函数名：<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>重定向</strong></p><p>文件描述符| 文件名|    类型|硬件<br>–|–|–|–|–<br>0|stdin|标准输入文件|键盘<br>1|stdout|标准输出文件|显示器<br>2|stderr|标准错误输出文件|显示器</p><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">输出重定向<br>标准输出重定向  <span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> &gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">file</span><br>标准错误输处重定向 <span class="hljs-keyword">command</span>  <span class="hljs-number">2</span>&gt;<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span><br>正确输出和错误信息同时保存<span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> &gt;<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>&gt;&amp;<span class="hljs-number">1</span>  把正确输出和错误信息同时保存到同一个文件（<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span>）中<br><span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> &gt;file1 <span class="hljs-number">2</span>&gt;file2把正确的输出结果输出到 file1 文件中，把错误信息输出到 file2 文件中<br><br>输出重定向的完整写法其实是fd&gt;<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span>或者fd&gt;&gt;<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span>，其中 fd 表示文件描述符，如果不写，默认为 <span class="hljs-number">1</span>，也就是标准输出文件<br>当文件描述符为 <span class="hljs-number">1</span> 时，一般都省略不写,文件描述符为大于 <span class="hljs-number">1</span> 的值时，比如 <span class="hljs-number">2</span>，就必须写上,如：<span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>&gt;<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span><br>fd和&gt;之间不能有空格，否则 Shell 会解析失败；&gt;和<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span>之间的空格可有可无，如 <span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">file</span><br>/dev/null   任何放入该文件的数据都会被丢弃，不能恢复（可以看作垃圾箱）<br><br>输入重定向<br><span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span>将 <span class="hljs-keyword">file</span> 文件中的内容作为 <span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> 的输入<br><span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> &lt;&lt;END从标准输入（键盘）中读取数据，直到遇见分界符 END 才停止（分界符可以是任意的字符串，用户自己定义）<br><span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> &lt;file1 &gt;file2将 file1 作为 <span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> 的输入，并将 <span class="hljs-keyword">command</span> 的处理结果输出到 file2<br><br>输入重定向的完整写法是fd&lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">file</span>，其中 fd 表示文件描述符，如果不写，默认为 <span class="hljs-number">0</span>，也就是标准输入文件<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
